KISS Kids (2014) (Digital) (DR & Quinch-Empire)


Trade paperback collecting the KISS Kids mini-series.

Presenting the adventures of Li'l Demon, Starchild, Catkid, and Spacey... the KISS Kids gang! This rockin' new comic offers adventures for all ages (and many in-jokes and familiar characters for the KISS faithful, too). No blood or fire here, just laughs and fun tales of the little costumed maniacs and the crazy town in which they live. Also features an all-new introduction from the ageless Gene "Lil Demon" Simmons and Paul "Starchild" Stanley!
